net.sf.JRecord.def.IO.builders

Interface ISchemaIOBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    INewLineCreator
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Icb2xmlIOBuilder, Icb2xmlMultiFileIOBuilder, ICobolIOBuilder, ICobolMultiCopybookIOBuilder, ICsvIOBuilder, IFileIOBuilder, IFixedWidthIOBuilder, IIOBuilder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CobolSchemaReader

    public interface ISchemaIOBuilder
extends INewLineCreator
    This interface defines a minimal IOBuilder. It is the parent of all other IOBuilders and is used to create a IOBuilder from an existing schema 
         JRecordInterface1.SCHEMA.newIOBuilder(existingSchema);
    Author:
    Bruce Martin
